Cyberpunk style: A towering server rack rendered as a neon-lit mechanical fortress, with multiple glowing disk arrays arranged in a geometric pattern resembling a futuristic cityscape. Holographic data streams flow between different sections like luminous rivers - some channels dedicated to separate pathways, others merging into massive storage blocks. The rack pulses with electric blue and hot magenta energy, with distinct zones clearly separated by glowing barriers. Fiber optic cables snake through the structure like veins of light. The scene is set against a dark industrial backdrop with rain-slicked surfaces reflecting the brilliant glow. Steam rises from cooling vents while small diagnostic drones hover around the structure, performing maintenance. The overall composition suggests immense power, careful organization, and high-speed data flow through a carefully architected system.
